2. STOREFRONT - Product Listing & Search
================================================================================
File: public/products.php

WORKFLOW:
1. User enters search term in header search bar
2. As user types (min 2 chars, 180ms debounce):
   a. AJAX call to /api/search_suggestions.php?q={term}
   b. AbortController cancels previous request
   c. Dropdown shows results with thumbnail, name, SKU, category
   d. Keyboard navigation: arrow keys, Enter to select, Escape to close
3. On form submit or suggestion click -> /products.php?q={term}
4. Server calls site_get_products(null, $search, 48)
5. Up to 48 products rendered in 3-column grid
6. Each card: image, name, price, favorites heart, "View details" link

USER INTERACTIONS:
- Type in search bar -> predictive suggestions dropdown
- Click suggestion -> navigate to product page
- Submit search -> products listing filtered
- Click "View details" -> /product.php?id={id}
- Click heart -> favorites system

