24. ADMIN - Product Import (CSV)
================================================================================
File: public/assets/js/admin.js
API: /api/import.php

THREE IMPORT TYPES:

A. IMPORT PRODUCTS:
1. Click "Import Products" button
2. Modal opens with: Mode (Add New / Update Existing), CSV file input, Example download
3. Download example CSV: /uploads/examples/import-products-example.csv
4. Select CSV file
5. Click "Import"
6. POST /api/import.php with FormData: csv file, importType='products', mode
7. Add mode: creates new products (skips existing SKUs)
8. Update mode: updates existing products by SKU (skips new)
9. Required for add: name, category, sku
10. Response: {created, updated, skipped, errors[], total}
11. Summary displayed in modal

B. IMPORT VARIANTS:
1. Click "Import Variants" button
2. Same modal flow
3. CSV must include: parentSku (matches to product), sku, name
4. POST /api/import.php with importType='variants'
5. Variant linked to parent product by parentSku lookup

